  "remarks": "Kurganpribor is a Russian military industry company. It provides weapons to the Ministry of Defence of the Russian Federation under the State defence order. It produces fuses for tank shots, land and naval artillery, multiple rocket launcher systems, and anti-aircraft missile systems.",
